  "text": "Hello, my name is Bianca. Let me tell you about my morning. I am at home, and I am looking out the window. The sky is grey and cloudy. It is raining now, and the wind is cold. I am drinking a hot coffee in the kitchen. My daughter is reading a book on the sofa. Today is not a sunny day, so I am wearing a warm jacket. I do not like the rain, but I love a calm morning at home.",
