  "file": "a9_listening1.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi, I am Rodrigo. I want to tell you about the seasons in my city. We have four seasons. In summer it is very hot, and the sun is strong every day. In winter it is cold, and the wind is strong. In spring the weather is warm, and many flowers open. My favorite season is autumn, because it is not hot and not cold. Right now it is spring, and today it is sunny. I am happy, because I love a sunny day.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a9_listening2.mp3"
 },
 {
